        <header>
          <h1 class="logo">XIM APEX</h1>
        </header>
        <figure>
                  </figure>
        <main>
                    <p class="large-8 large-centered" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #999999;">Welcome to XIM Technologies – the official site of <b><span style="color: #b62223;">XIM </span></b>advanced gaming input adapters!</span></p>
<p class="large-8 large-centered" style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #999999;"><span style="color: #b62223;"><b>XIM APEX</b></span> provides the </span><span style="color: #b62223;"><strong>highest precision mouse </strong><span style="color: #999999;">and</span><strong> keyboard</strong></span><span style="color: #999999;"> (and more) experience on <span style="color: #b62223;"><strong>Xbox One<span style="color: #999999;">,</span></strong> <strong>PlayStation 4 (PS4)</strong></span>, <span style="color: #ffffff;"><span style="color: #b62223;"><strong>Xbox 360</strong></span><span style="color: #999999;">,</span></span> and <span style="color: #b62223;"><strong>PlayStation 3 (PS3)</strong><span style="color: #999999;">. Unsurpassed by quality, ease-of-use, and flexibility, XIM is the perfect companion to the even most demanding gamer.</span></span></span></p>
<p class="large-8 large-centered" style="text-align: center; color: #999999;">XIM gamers all over the world enjoy gaming with their friends on consoles while they use the input method that suits them best.</p>
<p class="large-8 large-centered" style="text-align: center; color: #e9b500;">XIM APEX is scheduled for release in Q1 2018. Learn more <a href="http://community.xim.tech/index.php?topic=3819.msg641775#msg641775" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.<br />
Add yourself to our waiting list <a href="http://store.xim4.com/XIM-APEX_p_18.html">here</a>.</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-326" src="http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Diag.png" alt="" width="2750" height="1500" srcset="http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Diag.png 2750w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Diag-300x164.png 300w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Diag-768x419.png 768w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Diag-1024x559.png 1024w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Diag-640x349.png 640w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Diag-1500x818.png 1500w" sizes="(max-width: 1199px) 98vw, 1500px" /></p>
