    <section id="what-is-xim" class="light section" style="background-image: url(http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/background-light.png)">
  <article class="center">
    <figure>
      <img src="http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Top-1500x501.png" class="attachment-fp-large size-fp-large wp-post-image" alt="" srcset="http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Top-1500x501.png 1500w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Top-300x100.png 300w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Top-768x257.png 768w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Top-1024x342.png 1024w, http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/XIM-APEX-Top-640x214.png 640w" sizes="(max-width: 1199px) 98vw, 1500px" />    </figure>
    <header>
      <h1>XIM Enables Gamers</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <p>XIM enables a gamer to choose input devices that suits them best – whether you come from a PC or console background or if you game at a desk or couch in the living room. Its hardware compatibility doesn’t stop at just mice and keyboards. Support is also included for devices that provide the benefits of analog (thumbstick) for player movement combined with high fidelity aiming with a mouse. Mix and match different devices for your optimal playing style. Visit our <a href="http://xim.tech/xim/gaming-styles">Gaming Styles</a> page for more details. XIM also supports gamers with disabilities so that they can enjoy console gaming with others. Check out our <a href="http://xim4.com/hardware">Hardware Compatibility</a> list for our expanding set of support devices.</p>
                </main>
        <footer>
      <a class="button" href="http://xim.tech/shop/">Order Now</a>
    </footer>
      </article>
</section>
<section class="dark section section-aside" style="background-image: url(http://xim.tech/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/xim-mouse.jpg)">
  <article>
    <main>
      <header>
        <h1>Benefits of XIM</h1>
      </header>
      <ul>
<li>Next-generation console input adapter</li>
<li>Game on your Xbox One, PlayStation 4, Xbox 360 or PlayStation 3 using your favorite PC gaming-grade hardware</li>
<li>Supports both desktop and living room gaming styles</li>
<li>Mice, Keyboards, Joysticks, and Gameboard compatibility</li>
<li>Unsurpassed in-game 1-to-1 feel thanks to advanced <em>Smart Translator</em> technology</li>
<li>Simple real-time smartphone and tablet-based configuration</li>
<li>Real-time feedback to guide you to your optimal settings</li>
<li>Supports your existing Xbox headsets and chatpads</li>
<li>Firmware upgradable</li>
<li>Active community forum</li>
</ul>
